    Scope and Contents
Quarterly and final reports of project to evaluate ten community residential programs and two social centers for the chronically medical ill administered by the Illinois Dept. of Mental Health and Developmental Disabilities.  Reports include background and results of report, statistics on the entry, discharge, improvement of clients, evaluations of centers by clients and staff and samples of interview and evaluation forms.  
  
